il無成本又可以玩野，why not?</blockquote><br />\n有冇方法搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d1836cb31b09557d5932be7ab151af4a8e7205","tid":264701,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>報啦<br />\n海關唔查唔通你查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家諗緊仲有咩可以做</blockquote><br />\nsend封email無成本又可以玩野，why not?</blockquote><br />\n有冇方法搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生果報<br />\n但其實都未必會攪<br />\n始終好多公司都咁做<br />\n唔夠話題性傳媒好少插手<br />\n<br />\n而且佢話台灣進口都吹佢唔漲<br />\n大陸造完運去台灣<br />\n台灣再運黎香港<br />\n即係台灣進口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca940b1efac3919600690d70d432a06480ef627","tid":264701,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>報啦<br />\n海關唔查唔通你查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家諗緊仲有咩可以做</blockquote><br />\nsend封email無成本又可以玩野，why not?</blockquote><br />\n有冇方法搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公司仔真係難d&hellip;又無咩新聞價值"},{"pid":"80743b1d3d283cee119e78b18946004421e9f888","tid":264701,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>報啦<br />\n海關唔查唔通你查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家諗緊仲有咩可以做</blockquote><br />\nsend封email無成本又可以玩野，why not?</blockquote><br />\n有冇方法搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生果報<br />\n但其實都未必會攪<br />\n始終好多公司都咁做<br />\n唔夠話題性傳媒好少插手<br />\n<br />\n而且佢話台灣進口都吹佢唔漲<br />\n大陸造完運去台灣<br />\n台灣再運黎香港<br />\n即係台灣進口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n屌 佢真係玩晒<br />\n<br />\n依家最不滿係佢d公關手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，好似d仆街美容院咁，見負皮就del comment ，跟手blacklist，開左十幾個Facebook account 無一幸免，唔面對問題都算，仲要咁樣打壓，連登開post都逃唔出佢嘅打擊，以前試過facebook開page，幾野就比佢舉報到刪page，我決定唔可以就咁當無事，佢刪一次我開一次"},{"pid":"72ae8f9f5e19eb30b8222fa6a74a9be5835b77aa","tid":264701,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I4ZBb4E-6PQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI4ZBb4E-6PQ&d=syoTitLUGbK4biM2OqKsmgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=468b2b9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I4ZBb4E-6PQ</a> <br />\n附上黑心老板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊有人想非禮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1653c77aa7044c7cb7973dbb1f6d42601f63a5c5","tid":264701,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2448f56f84d26c68e93ca4120165a10b3bb450e6","tid":264701,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0f6dca48c705638ae58cdc904654dec7a84bb9ea","tid":264701,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1fb7d3b55f74987ec4e6f61878b5e27cd0bde06e","tid":264701,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:28:37.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"40bbd6e93d0887c9c4db97ab19527fe6bc5f6edb","tid":264701,"uid":97166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"5"}]}